OL,5, Thomas Hebbron is one of the forgotten 
OL,6, victims of the pandemic.               
OL,8,FHe was diagnosed with leukaemia in     
OL,9,FFebruary 2019 - a year before Covid hit
OL,10,Fthe UK.                                
OL,12,FThe eight-year-old, from Leeds, has    
OL,13,Fbeen treated with chemotherapy which   
OL,14,Fhas continued throughout the pandemic, 
OL,15,Fbut his health has suffered in other   
OL,16,Fways - and his mother believes the     
OL,17,Funrelenting focus on the virus is to   
OL,18,Fblame.                                 
